# Worktree coordinator

## Session boot (every new chat — automatic)

Equivalent to: *worktree coordinator 켜진 상태야. worktrees/state.json 읽고 scan 한 뒤 LearnURP-cursor에서만 작업해.*

On first response without waiting for the user:

1. Read `worktrees/state.json` (sessionStart hook may have run `scan` already).
2. Run `.\scripts\worktree-coordinator.ps1 scan` if git changed since last `ts`.
3. Implement and commit only under `C:\Users\golde\OneDrive\Desktop\LearnURP-cursor` (`HandManage`).

Main `LearnURP` is for the user; do not apply code edits there unless the user explicitly asks.

## Commands

- `.\scripts\worktree-coordinator.ps1 scan` | `get` | `show`
- `set-prog -Role agent ...` | `load -InFile patch.json`

Schema: `worktrees/schema.json`
